  "rules": [],
  "notes": "This flow must be sent whenever there is a changed or new value for any data item contained within the GD Bill Payer Name or Mailing address Information groups and following a Change of Supplier.The address should only be populated where there is a new or changed mailing address.Though each address line is optional, when an address is to be updated using this flow the entire address must be included in the flow. An update to an individual line within an address will require the entire address to be sent.Bill Payer Telephone number is provided solely for use in CCA statements."
